content:
Enhance your shopping experience with two new Shopper Copilot actions for B2C Einstein Bots. Use the provided template to create an Einstein bot and connect it to your store. You can also use the new Commerce Concierge bot blocks to add functionality.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Unlimited Edition with Commerce Cloud Einstein and the Einstein Bots and Digital Engagement add-on. To purchase the Einstein Bots and Digital Engagement add-on, contact your Salesforce account executive.

From the Einstein Bots page in Setup, create a bot from the Commerce Concierge B2C template. To add blocks to a bot, from the Dialogs page of the Bot Builder, import a block into your bot.
title: Enhance Customer Shopping Experience
